{"tid":2445811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白登偽政府多次秘密接觸北韓　至今未獲回應","createTime":"2021-03-14T02:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T00:55:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"526ed918e9ce3b755aa30bb0d688f9cce2991d44","tid":2445811,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:43:21.000Z","msg":"美國一名高級官員上周六（13日）向英國傳媒透露，拜登政府自上月中開始試圖秘密接觸北韓政府，但至今未獲回應。<br />\n<br />\n該官員表示，華府試圖循數個外交途徑接觸平壤，包括北韓駐聯合國使團，均未獲回應，他拒絕評論朝方的沉默會如何影響拜登政府檢視北韓政策。外界關注北韓無視美方招手，華府會如何處理朝核問題，相信會成為美國與日本的外長防長「2+2」安全會議焦點議題。<br />\n<br />\n拜登政府料下月內完成檢視對朝政策，國務卿布林肯曾揚言不排除對北韓實施更多制裁及外交手段。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20210314/photo/bkn-20210314091809458-0314_00992_001_01p.jpg?20210314100657\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fintnews%2F20210314%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210314091809458-0314_00992_001_01p.jpg%3F20210314100657&h=c064f00b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北韓過往試射火星15型洲際彈道導彈的情況。<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on. cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20210314/bkn-20210314091809458-0314_00992_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"a9ee1bb8078169fc8fdb5022f37ab007985478c1","tid":2445811,"uid":60535,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:48:34.000Z","msg":"金仔：你搞我老死，我緊係唔理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1576a049351a1a75b4af8ff3a350c6e7ca9921","tid":2445811,"uid":151074,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:52:23.000Z","msg":"預左打仲有乜好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a965e54d19f5e050142a9744acf54f8dbfe208","tid":2445811,"uid":117509,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"a9ee1bb8078169fc8fdb5022f37ab007985478c1","tid":2445811,"uid":60535,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:48:34.000Z","msg":"金仔：你搞我老死，我緊係唔理你<img src=\"/as